messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to repent of the spirit of lust I want to repent of adultery and fornication i want Jesus to take the spirit of adultery and fornication out of me I pray for restoration and true salvation I want to be released from the spirit of the world I want to live in line with God's word I want to repent of aligning my will with the will of Satan and I want to break off all agreements with Satan and I want total healing and restoration from the will of Satan I repent of all the sins I have committed in this body I need the spirit of God to break off everything related to Satan off of my life
